{"tid":372982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑","createTime":"2017-08-24T16:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T12:09:04.000Z","uid":11512,"like":123,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f10e5bcbcce8744aa5b099b4e8ef2cdd02126b29","tid":372982,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈曼首名有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先賓咩加,唔好玩啦 葡萄牙野，6分穩陣<br />\n<br />\n巴素利,,如果係巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又6分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又6分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 盧卡古,華舒福,MK仔,馬斯亞 加上關鍵王連加特.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n18分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"2b2d30041bcf437268317e01eb5997eccf7c3496","tid":372982,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf2c1cabda37a35d27e827a97701f077962a3cb","tid":372982,"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"中兩隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad89cd91d9c392cd6923b3431f2ca3ed736333d","tid":372982,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"又保送"},{"pid":"b6e9c27204a0be576ca95681f1948f8efcf01ed8","tid":372982,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"唔係內定都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0dc4072ec9e5bc796283cdc6139bea3c345b19","tid":372982,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:43:45.000Z","msg":